  _entries:
  - _unitData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fc3212549ea209a43808179ddb75e0cf, type: 2}
    _hintDescription: Reflects damage back. Low-HP units will kill themselves attacking it
  - _unitData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b4ceb00dbc4a00d449eb013f15d1e0f2, type: 2}
    _hintDescription: Jumps to your backline. Protect ranged units or they'll be picked off first.
  - _unitData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 00c66e23a74199641b819908e99f0e14, type: 2}
    _hintDescription: Fireballs deal area damage. Counter with high-HP units.
  - _unitData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c7dcd16282e47e144bf71f3d27a51fd7, type: 2}
    _hintDescription: Fast, high damage single target. Shreds tanks but struggles against crowds.
  - _unitData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6763abca2369a4b4ea6b55fffa9c4421, type: 2}
    _hintDescription: Slow but very strong. Swarm it with many units.
  - _unitData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3a3aaf4003b88ac4d8b4900ec11da21f, type: 2}
    _hintDescription: Summons skeleton warriors over time. Kill it fast before you're overwhelmed.
  - _unitData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6b185bead6ff80042b77d7439df8eff5, type: 2}
    _hintDescription: "Launches a spear volley before joining the fight. Survive the first strike.\n"
